[2026-03-26] ## ✅ Fixed JavaScript Errors!

**Changes deployed:** Commit `cc1f59f`

### What Was Wrong:

You had **two competing AI chat systems** running at the same time:
1. **Old system** in `script.js` - looking for DOM elements that don't exist
2. **New sidebar system** in `split-screen-sync.js` - the modern sidebar UI

This caused the error: `Cannot read properties of null (reading 'addEventListener')` because `script.js` was trying to attach event listeners to elements that were never created.

